        {
            "title": "轉機？Snap股價腰斬創一年新低 分析師齊砍目標價 但RSI浮現超賣訊號",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uKbqUEDTSRtb1VKuoUmLMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F-snap%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E8%85%B0%E6%96%AC%E5%89%B5-%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E9%BD%8A%E7%A0%8D%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B9-%E4%BD%86rsi%E6%B5%AE%E7%8F%BE%E8%B6%85%E8%B3%A3%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F-202051296.html",
