        {
            "title": "戰爭刺激避險情緒升溫 交易員今年年初以來首次看好美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Commodity Futures Trading Commission, Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"714\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4Cyl02bscPNn6SeVq8oQjw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9aeb4a77e8476eeab81e9f9b026be639\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Commodity Futures Trading Commission, Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著中東戰爭推高能源成本，美元避險地位獲得支撐，交易員今年首次看漲美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">商品期貨交易委員會(CFTC)周五公佈的數據顯示，截至3月 17日，對沖基金、資產管理公司和其他投機者已持有價值62億美元的美元多頭頭寸。他們此前自12月中旬以來一直押注美元走弱。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"714\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.hM7fwXWCx8takgHFat1DQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bc6ad33d73c8d94be617c230ffdea7df\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這標志著自美國襲擊伊朗三周以來，日交易量達9.5萬億美元的外匯市場情緒發生轉變。除了油價上漲之外， 彭博美元指數3月份上漲約2%，邁向自7月以來最大的月度漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-da011f63-8f25-326c-bbf4-8ca682c7d352-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據CFTC的數據，投機交易員在2月中旬積累了約220億美元的空頭頭寸，現在已經開始逐步撤回。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「突發事件會讓投資者在初期階段風險承受力下降，這意味著他們會拋售美元空頭頭寸，」BMO資產管理公司的Bipan Rai表示：「但高流動性和避險屬性應該有助於美元走強。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元現貨指數周五上漲0.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Traders Turn Positive on US Dollar for First Time This Year (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Carter Johnson.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
